description: The FiiO L10 is designed with a 3.5mm stereo jack to Apple's dock connector, enabling output of high quality line-level audio from iPod, iPhone, and iPad that can be sent to portable audio equipment such as headphone amplifiers and power amplifiers. Designed with high-quality materials, the L10 isolates the audio signal from interference to deliver cleaner and more accurate sound from your iPod/iPhone/iPad.Feature Highlights- Shielded construction provides maximum isolation from interference- Pure copper conductors for better audio clarity and a more natural-sounding midrange- High quality durable connectors for precise contact and signal integrity- Supports standard dock profile on iPod, iPhone, and iPad. Does not support Shuffle.SpecificationsLength: 50cm (20-Inch)Wire Diameter: 3mmWire Gauge: AWG-18Wire Material: Oxygen Free CopperImpedance: Max 0.5 OhmInsulation: Min 2M OhmWire Jacket: PVC
title: FiiO L10 20-Inch Line Out Dock (LOD) Cable For iPod and iPhone
